data.description: Looking for the best of both worlds - the tranquility of your surroundings and the convenience of being close to top-tier amenities, fine dining, high-end shopping, and renowned schools? This meticulously maintained residence presents an rare opportunity to own 0.64acres with covered RV parking and a workshop with sheds in a well established neighborhood. Its unique blend of updates, custom original features, absence of mello roos and prime location make it a incredible opportunity to make your own. It's a place that promises to captivate those with a love for the outdoors and auto enthusiasts alike. Let's work together to see how we can call 4449 Pomo Circle YOUR home. Sellers are willing to offer credit to buy down rate:)
